.Dt GDROM 4 dreamcast
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm gdrom
.Nd GD-ROM disk driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "gdrom0 at shb?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the Dreamcast CD-ROM
.Pq Dq GD-ROM
storage device.
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width /dev/rgdromXXXX -compact
